If, while reading this book, you have specific questions
on the command-line interface of [[5i]] or on the related
\plan debuggers, I suggest you to consult the manual pages
in my \plan repository: [[docs/man/1/vi]] for [[5i]]
itself, and [[docs/man/1/db]] for the [[db]] debugger
