<<[[Idp0()]] trace>>=
if(trace)
    itrace("%s%s\tR%d,R%d,R%d =#%x",
        reg.ip->name, cond[reg.instr_cond],
        rm, rn, rd,
        reg.r[rd]);
@
\fi



%claude:
The [<dpex()>] function (``data processing execute'')
is where the actual arithmetic or logic operation happens.
It takes the two operands [[o1]] and [[o2]] (already
extracted and shifted by the caller) and switches on
the 4-bit opcode to perform the right operation:

